snippet.title: Hovership Havoc Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/p/hovership-havoc/9np9n9jzv55t

Pre-Order Now On Xbox One. Available January 17, 2020!

Available Now On Steam
https://store.steampowered.com/app/872040/Hovership_Havoc/

Hovership Havoc is a randomly generated twin-stick shooter with 3rd person boss battles. Upgrade your Hovership and obtain randomly dropped abilities to help destroy robotic enemies in a futuristic factory environment.

Available now on Steam
Coming to Xbox One in Summer 2019

http://www.hovershiphavoc.com/
https://twitter.com/snowdaysoftware
